I was surprise that printing cost has increase that much.
Printing from email additional $1 on top of printing 1 piece non colour (BW) which cost $0.80.
Meaning if print 1 copy BW from email will cost u $1.80.

If u want to save $1, remember to save to thumb drive.

Do not ever collect your parcel from here. I had 5 parcels to collect and she only passed me 4. When I asked her if she could check if she still had another of my parcel she started screaming at me saying it's not her problem and that I was in the wrong. I tried explaining to her but she just started screaming at me more. Shoppe shows the parcel has been collected and I've double checked my items. Some serious attitude problems.

Managed to collect my shopee parcel today. Checked with the Aunty for operating hours:
Mon-Fri: closed at 8pm
Saturday: closed at 2pm
Sunday & PH: closed
google states 9-9pm. came down all the way from work to find that the place already closed at 815pm. what a waste of time!
